original_title: Sesame Street: Elmo's World: Elmo Has Two!  Hands, Ears & Feet
overview: Listen closely, it's a finger-snapping, toe-tapping good time. With help from Mr. Noodle, Rosita, Baby Bear and everyone's favorite goldfish Dorothy, Elmo finds out all the different things his body can do as he plays patty cake, hops on one foot, wiggles his ears and more.
title: Sesame Street: Elmo's World: Elmo Has Two!  Hands, Ears & Feet
